 by other covariates. This modelling approach should\nprove useful for marine spatial planners in siting OWEDs while considering key\nhabitats and areas potentially vulnerable to anthropogenic stressors. Moreover,\nthe approach is equally suitable for terrestrial or aquatic systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 May 2017 18:13:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-03"}
