t_{1}^{x}\\frac{M(u)}{u^{\\kappa}}du$ under the weak Mertens\nHypothesis. We also have $\\Omega$-result of this integral unconditionally, and\nso we find that the upper bound which is obtained in this paper of this\nintegral is the best possible estimation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 May 2017 08:39:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Jun 2017 10:12:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-23"}
